title: War of the Roses: She Kept Trying To Get Into His Phone
description: Angela thinks her boyfriend, Dee, is cheating. He doesn't respond to a lot of texts, so she decided to watch him like a hawk so that she could try and get into his phone to see what was going on. What she found once she did will blow your mind!
